This is a CakePHP Datasource for accessing the Twilio API via standard model functions in CakePHP.



REQUIREMENTS
-----------------
PHP 5.x
CakePHP 1.3.x (may work on 1.2 but haven't tested)


INSTALL
-----------------

1. Just add the files to a new CakePHP Project.
2. edit the database file and use your credentials.
3. modify the texts controller to your needs and voila!